# 2. Requirement Analysis 

## Functional Requirements

* Upload and read the dataset.
* Perform preprocessing.
* Handle missing values.
* Train a Linear Regression model.
* Save the trained model.
* Accept user inputs through a web form.
* Predict Human Development Index.
* Display prediction results.

## Non-Functional Requirements

* User-friendly interface.
* Fast prediction response.
* Reliable prediction accuracy.
* Easy maintenance.
* Scalability.

## Software Requirements

* Python 3.x
* Visual Studio Code
* Flask
* NumPy
* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Seaborn
* Scikit-learn
* Pickle

## Hardware Requirements

* Intel Core i3 or higher
* 4 GB RAM or above
* Windows/Linux/macOS
* 500 MB free disk space

## Dataset Requirements

* HDI Dataset
* CSV Format
* Kaggle/Open Data Source

## Expected Output

Prediction of Human Development Index based on user-provided socio-economic indicators.
